nodes.text: A form of alchemy was performed by the Je'daii ranger Lanoree Brock her spare time; creating a living being from cells. Checking on it, she noticed blood dribbled from forming veins, vestigial limbs flapped around and it had milky eyes. Brock had created it from her own flesh. In the early stages, it had no mind and Lanoree wondered if it could feel pain.
